snippet.title: The Game of Life (PS1) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A playthrough of Hasbro's 1998 board game adaptation for the Sony Playstation, The Game of Life. 

It's essentially the same thing as the boardgame, but loaded with small minigames, hideously fugly CGI cutscenes, and lots of random but funky music. It's entertaining in short bursts.
_______
No cheats were used during the recording of this video. 

NintendoComplete (http://www.nintendocomplete.com/) punches you in the face with in-depth reviews, screenshot archives, and music from classic 8-bit NES games!
